Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, and more.

Get Started Using CRM Analytics by going mobile with it, setting up the platform, integrating data, gaining insights directly at source, exploring and visualizing your data, building dashboards, embedding and customizing, creating and sharing apps to give business users a bigger picture, deploying industry apps and prebuilt apps, managing templated apps, and more.

The Self-Service Embedded Dashboard offers a comprehensive view of account-specific details such as contracts, quotes, orders, bills, and asset distribution. It integrates into the community portal or SMB Console for procurement managers and small and medium business executives to access self-service analytics for a 360Â° view of the complete account.

This dashboard tracks and analyzes contracts, assesses case distribution, highlights overdue bills, shows pending quotes, gains visibility into order distribution, and provides a comprehensive view of asset allocation and distribution with geographic insights.
title: Self-Service Embedded Dashboard in Salesforce
